Ga wani ɗan gajeren jawabi a West Virginia, a YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara yakin neman zabensa a wannan yammacin a birnin Wheeling, na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne jawabi na farko cikin jawabai biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya haɗa da tsayawa a wuraren da ake ganin sun fi kusa da shi, kamar su Tennessee da Mississippi.
A zaben da ya amince da dakatar da takarar da ya zaba a kan babban kotun, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisa a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi jawabin Trump a yammacin Virginia kuma ta yaya za a iya kallonsa a kan intanet?
Za a yi jawabi a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia, da ƙarfe 7 na yamma, ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump a West Virginia a YouTube a nan.
Trump zai iya yin magana game da wanda zai tsaya takara a kotun koli na wannan makon, Brett Kavanaugh, saboda ya yi matukar damuwa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, lokacin da majalisar dattawa ta amince da dakatar da takarar har tsawon mako guda, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan kamfen shine don taimakawa 'yan Republican su sami wasu ƙarfi a gaban zaben na Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, masu fafutukar shugaban kasa Trump sun ce manufar tarurrukan su biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito, shine karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon bayan Republican a kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da wakilai.
"Samun iko da majalisa na da muhimmanci a ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka zai ziyarci jihohi da dama domin ya fara zafin kakar zabe", in ji mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda bai so a bayyana sunansa ba.
Jawabin da ake shirin yi a filin wasa na Westbank a birnin Vigil yana da bukatar masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma 'yan jarida a birnin Pittsburgh, in ji Metro News na jihar West Virginia.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan jiya a jihar West Virginia, inda ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da ya kada a zaben 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar Sanata na West Virginia, Republican Patrick Morrissey, wanda yake cikin kasa-kasa a kan kuri'un da ake gudanarwa.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don ya tura shi zuwa saman darajar", in ji Simon Haider, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
