Jim Furyck yana bukatar maki takwas daga wasannin 12 da za a yi a ranar Lahadi don ya ci nasara.
Fleetwood sun kasance farkon 'yan wasan Turai da suka samu maki hudu a jere, lokacin da suka yi ninki biyu tare da Molinari a "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai kayatarwa, kuma sun kasance kawai na biyu da suka sami maki huɗu a cikin wasanninsu huɗu na farko a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup.
