Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin fargaba ta hanyar tallata farfaganda
Makon daya bayan jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani talla mai shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka, wanda ya yi watsi da amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da shafin jaridar Des Moines Register da ake sayarwa a jihar Iowa, inda ya zargi China da kokarin yin tasiri a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Tashin hankalin Trump kan kokarin da Beijing ke yi na shafar zaben Amurka, na nuna wani sabon mataki na kara tsanantawa a yakin neman matsin lamba kan kasar Sin, in ji jami'an Amurka ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Ko da yake yana da kyau gwamnatocin ƙasashen waje su yi talla don su ƙarfafa kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington suna faɗa cikin yaƙin cinikayya da ke ƙaruwa, kuma suna kokawa a kan haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
A cewar masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka, an yi amfani da tarar da kasar Sin ta yi wa masu fitar da kayayyaki a Iowa da makamancin haka, wadanda suka goyi bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican.
Terry Branstad  jakadan Amurka a China, tsohon gwamnan Iowa kuma daya daga cikin manyan masu fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin  ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kasuwanci.
A cikin wani labarin da aka wallafa a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya ce, China ta ƙara yin rashin hankali ta wajen buga tallace-tallace a cikin 'yan jaridarmu.
"A cikin yada farfagandar, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da kuma 'yancin manema labarai da ake girmamawa a Amurka, ta kuma ba da sanarwar tallace-tallace da aka biya", in ji Branstad.
"A halin yanzu, a cikin gidan jaridar Beijing na gida, ba za ku sami muryoyin adawa da juna ba kuma ba za ku sami ainihin hoto ba wanda ke nuna ra'ayoyi daban-daban da mutanen China ke da su game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China mai ban tsoro, saboda jaridar tana ƙarƙashin matsin lamba na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
Branstad ya kuma kara da cewa wasu manyan jaridun kasar Sin sun ki amincewa da buga labarinsa, amma bai bayyana ko wane ne ba.
Masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa, a lokacin da ake gab da zaben, wani dan takarar Republican ya hana Kavanaugh cin zabe.
Duk da cewa shugabannin jam'iyyar Republican da dama sun kasance masu aminci ga mai neman kujerar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zargi da laifuffukan cin zarafin mata, wani manazarci ya yi gargadin cewa hakan zai jawo martani mai tsanani a zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata.
Yanayin ya sa mutane su yi mamaki sosai, kuma 'yan Republican da yawa sun riga sun bayyana cewa suna son su yi zabe.
"Ba za ka iya cire irin waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a jaridar The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa kiran da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi na minti na karshe na bude binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, za su tuna da shi gobe da kuma a watan Nuwamba", in ji jaridar Washington, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ra'ayin ci gaba ta "MoveOn" Karine Jean-Pierre a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun yi ihu suna cewa: "Laraba ta kusa!" a lokacin zanga-zangar a harabar majalisar dattawa, lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar nada Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, kamar yadda Mic ya ruwaito.
"Himma da himma na dimokiradiyya za su ratsa ƙasashe", in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai sharhi kan siyasa a shafin yanar gizon labarai.
Mutane suna cewa ta riga ta kasance mai ƙarfi, kuma suna da gaskiya.
Amma za ta iya ƙara ƙarfafa matsayi, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa ƙuri'a a cikin yankunan karkara da kuma masu jefa ƙuri'a 'yan shekara 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa ƙuri'a.
Ko da kafin Ch.B. Ford ta ba da shaida a fili, inda ta yi bayani dalla-dalla game da zargin cin zarafin da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli, manazarta sun ce idan 'yan Republican suka amince da takarar, hakan na iya haifar da fushi.
"Wannan ya haifar da babbar damuwa ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa Michael Steele, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun kwamitin ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe, ba wai kawai ko Kavanaugh zai zama alkalin ba, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka gudanar da lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da Ch.B. Ford", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan kungiyar 'Yan Democrat a Amurka, a wani jawabi da ya bayar ga tashar labarai.
Duk da haka, jama'ar Amirka ba su yarda da abin da za su yi imani da shi ba bayan da Kavanaugh da Ch.B. Ford suka nuna, ko da yake ta sami goyon baya.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun gaskata da nuna gaskiya ga Ch.B. Ford, kuma kashi 35 cikin 100 sun ce sun gaskata da Kavanaugh.
