Wanda ya kirkiro kafofin watsa labarai yana shirin kafa sabuwar intanet domin ya yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, yana kirkirar wani sabon kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan shahararren mai kirkiro shine Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ke aiki akan Berners-Lee's open source platform Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake ajiye bayanan su, da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar wannan bayanin.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce mamaye duniya.
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Solid wani app ne da ke aiki da fasaha wanda ke ba mutane damar gina shagon bayanan sirri na kan layi  POD.
Za a iya samun jerin abubuwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandarku, ɗakunan kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sirri ko na aiki.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya a lokaci guda.
Shagon yanar gizo na bayanan sirri na musamman ne saboda mai amfani ne kawai ke yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar bayanansa.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "samar da mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar John Bruce, shugaban kamfanin, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma basira da ake bukata domin kowa ya samu damar shiga kamfanin Solid.
A halin yanzu kamfanin ya ƙunshi T. Berners-Lee, J. Bruce Lee, IBM ta sayi dandalin tsaro, wasu masu shirye-shirye da aka hayar don yin aiki a kan wannan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a duk faɗin duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da abubuwan da aka samar a shafin Inrupt .
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su yarda da Facebook ko Google ba game da sauye-sauye da za su kawo sauyi a cikin tsarin kasuwancin su na yau da kullum.
Ba ma neman izininsu.
A cikin wani rahoto na Medium da aka fitar a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, Inrupt na da manufa ta samar da wutar lantarki da kuma yanayin halittu da za su taimaka wajen kare dorewa da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa mai suna Solid.
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet ta hanyar kafa Consortium na Media a Jami'ar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na intanet.
Ko da yake yana aiki tare da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma darektan Consortium na Sanarwa, Gidauniyar Sanarwa da Cibiyar Buɗe Bayanai.
"Ina jin kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
