Turai ta yi nasara a gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Tawagar Turai, bayan da ta doke tawagar Amurka da lambar karshe ta 16.5:10.5, ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 a Le Golf National dake kusa da Paris, Faransa.
Wannan shi ne karo na shida da Amurka ta ci kofin Turai a jere, kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder Cup a nahiyar ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin gasar ne bayan da kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya samu maki 14.5 wanda ya isa ya ci Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a gasar, ya yi ta buga kwallo daga filin wasa kai tsaye cikin ruwa a wasan 3 na 16 ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya F. Molinari ya yi fice a duk zagaye kuma ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka samu 5-0-0 tun 1979 lokacin da gasar ta dauki siffar ta yanzu.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sha kashi 5-4 a kan dan wasan da ya fi kasa a Turai Thorbjørn Olesen daga Denmark.
Dustin Johnson wanda ya fi kowacce a duniya, ya ci Ian Poulter da ci 2-1, wanda ya yi wasa da gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
Tsohon dan wasan gasar Ryder Cup takwas Sergio Garcia na Spain ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara a gasar, inda ya ci kwallaye 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
