A cikin 'Red Flood' labarai, a Painelas, Manaty da Sarasoto, yawan ruwan ya ragu
Wani sabon rahoto na Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida (FWC) ya ce yawan ruwan sama na Yellowfin tuna yana raguwa a yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an lura da karin fure a yankunan Painela, Manati, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier  wannan yana ba da damar ɗauka cewa ma'aunin yana raguwa.
Ruwan Tsufana ya kai kusan mil 130 daga bakin teku daga Pineellas da ke arewa zuwa Lee County da ke kudu.
Ana iya samun wuraren da aka yi tashin wutar a kusan mil 10 daga bakin tekun a gundumar Hillsborough, amma ba haka ba ne a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma samu ambaliyar ruwan sama a gundumar Easter.
A makon da ya gabata, an bayar da rahoton matsakaicin taro a gundumar Pineellas da ke kusa da tekun, a gundumar Hillsborough daga ƙasa zuwa sama, a gundumar Manatee daga ƙasa zuwa sama, a gundumar Sarasota da ke kusa da tekun daga ƙasa zuwa sama, a gundumar Charlotte daga ƙasa zuwa ciki, a gundumar Lee's daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, a gundumar Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni na kamuwa da cutar numfashi a gundumar Paines, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu wani rahoton tashin iska a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
